OL,6,FA DJ and his adopted sister who
OL,7,Fsexually abused children who attended
OL,8,Fdiscos have been jailed.
OL,10,FDarren Gibson and Rebecca Kirton, who
OL,11,Fwere in a relationship, were both
OL,12,Finvolved in grooming young victims in
OL,13,FLeeds between 2002 and 2008.
OL,15,FTwo of Gibson's victims were in their
OL,16,Fearly teens when he raped them in 2004.
OL,18,FHe exchanged numbers with one of the
OL,19,Fgirls and arranged for her to go to
OL,20,Fhis house the next day.
