OL,6,FShe went with a friend to the house,
OL,7,Fwhere Gibson and Kirton plied them
OL,8,Fwith drink.
OL,10,FAfter the friend was ill and was put
OL,11,Fto bed by Kirton, Gibson raped and
OL,12,Fsexually assaulted the victim.
OL,14,FThe second victim requested a song at
OL,15,Fa disco where Gibson was working as a
OL,16,FDJ. As she was leaving the stage he
OL,17,Fsexually assaulted her. The victim
OL,18,Fimmediately reported the incident to
OL,19,Fpolice.
