OL,4,Cjailed for grooming girls at discos
OL,6,FThe third victim was groomed over a
OL,7,Flonger period of time, from her pre-
OL,8,Fteens to her mid-teens. She was raped
OL,9,Fand sexually assaulted by Gibson, with
OL,10,FKirton joining in some of the abuse.
OL,12,FGibson, now 54, of Holdforth Close,
OL,13,FLeeds, was found guilty of 19 offences
OL,14,Fafter a trial in September, including
OL,15,Findecent assault, rape, sexual assault
OL,16,Fand causing or inciting a child into
OL,17,Fsexual activity.
OL,19,FHe was jailed for 24 years.
