OL,6,FKirton, 39, also of Holdforth Close,
OL,7,Fwas found guilty at trial of two
OL,8,Fcounts of sexual assault, one of rape
OL,9,Fand one of causing or inciting a child
OL,10,Finto sexual activity. She was jailed
OL,11,Ffor 12 years.
OL,13,FBoth were ordered to sign the sex
OL,14,Foffenders' register for life.
OL,16,FDet Insp Stephen King, of West
OL,17,FYorkshire Police's major investigation
OL,18,Freview team, praised the "courage and
OL,19,Fbravery" of the victims.
