OL,6,FHe said: "They have had to wait a long
OL,7,Ftime to see justice finally being done
OL,8,Fand I hope today's outcome will bring
OL,9,Fsome comfort to them.
OL,11,F"I'm pleased that in handing down
OL,12,Fthese sentences, the court has
OL,13,Frecognised the gravity of Gibson and
OL,14,FKirton's offending. They are
OL,15,Fcalculated sexual predators who
OL,16,Fcarried out serious harm to young
OL,17,Fgirls over a significant period of
OL,18,Ftime."
